[Field] (This card remains in your Battle Area until you place another [Field].)
[End of Your Turn] If you have 4 or less energy and you placed a card from your energy into its owner's Drop during this turn, add up to 1 card with a cost of 3 or more from your Drop to your energy in Rest Mode.
